data.description: Discover this stunning 3-bed, 2-bath home with a newer roof and A.C. system. Enjoy the luxury of an artesian well and an inviting in-ground  pool. Embrace the open concept split floor plan with walk-in closets in all of the bedrooms, and a walk-in pantry in the kitchen! Unleash your creativity with two versatile workshops - one charming as a cottage, the other perfect as a workshop. This double lot property is beautifully fenced and sits on a canal that leads to Lake Hatchineha with a sturdy seawall and two boat dock slips equipped with running water and electricity. Experience the epitome of space and beauty in this captivating home.
